  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CZO Online</strong> - This is a tactical multiplayer first-person shooter, the player has the opportunity to participate in multiplayer battles using many types of weapons in the arsenal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/88ccefff006af0ccc72aee5017379fa1.avif?t=1739469976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras_big/88ccefff006af0ccc72aee5017379fa1.avif?t=1739469976 width=800 height=448 /></span><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Customizer:</strong></u><br>All weapons can be cuztomized, included knifes, axes and grenades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ability to use cars, heavy combat techniques or call for backup:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/daf67cbe2e01d28803ca7923e82cf0f3.avif?t=1739469976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras_big/daf67cbe2e01d28803ca7923e82cf0f3.avif?t=1739469976 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crazy and funny dynamic gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/730662be48cbb73b4c1d6710c6d7b6b9.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/730662be48cbb73b4c1d6710c6d7b6b9.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/730662be48cbb73b4c1d6710c6d7b6b9.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/a840c6539c945bf329fbf1e599d5dfe8.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/a840c6539c945bf329fbf1e599d5dfe8.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/a840c6539c945bf329fbf1e599d5dfe8.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Possibilities:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7 game modes [<strong><u>Team Deathmatch, Capture To The Flag</u></strong>, <strong><u>Free For All</u></strong>, <strong><u>Counter Force</u></strong>, <strong><u>Cover Points</u></strong>, <strong><u>Gun Race</u></strong>, <strong><u>Bomb Defuse</u></strong>]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Multiplayer (up to 20 players)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- First/Third Person Camera View   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10 Maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Large selection of skins for player and weapon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- About 37 weapon models</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Vehicle supported [cars, tanks]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Kill streaks supported [Helicopter, Drone UAV , Missile Gust] </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Clans system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Level system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Progress system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Rating system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Advanced AI Bots</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Friends system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Chat system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Voice system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Loadout system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Weapon customization</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CZO Online</strong> - This is a tactical multiplayer first-person shooter, the player has the opportunity to participate in multiplayer battles using many types of weapons in the arsenal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/88ccefff006af0ccc72aee5017379fa1.avif?t=1739469976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras_big/88ccefff006af0ccc72aee5017379fa1.avif?t=1739469976 width=800 height=448 /></span><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Customizer:</strong></u><br>All weapons can be cuztomized, included knifes, axes and grenades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/